description:
OVERVIEW EXPERIENCE {****}
been here twice so far, both times during the day.  experience was much better the first time.

FOOD {****}
{+} good flavors
{+} different take on mexican, e.g. the quesidillas 
{-} too much cilantro and raw onions

DRINKS {**** 1/2}
{+} yummy & strong!

SERVICE {*** 1/2}
{+} 1st visit, server was very friendly and attentive
{-} 2nd visit server never came back after appetizers were dropped off (until the bill). She didn't deliver the main dishes (which meant she didn't ask if we needed anything else).  Also since she didn't come back, I didn't get a chance to order my second drink

ATMOSPHERE {****}
{+} cute
{+} clean
{+} casual
